== 製作 ==
[[File:Brenton_Thwaites.jpg|thumb]]領銜出演[[迪克·格雷森|理查·「迪克」·格雷森／羅賓／夜翼]]]]
=== 開發 ===
2014年9月，[[特納電視網|特納電視台]]宣佈啟動真人電視劇《泰坦》的製作計劃<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2014/tv/news/titans-dick-grayson-nighwing-tnt-1201303968/ |title=TNT Eyes ''Titans'' Superhero Series |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |first=Whitney |last=Friedlander |date=2014-09-11 |accessdate=2018-12-10 |language=en |archive-date=2018-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828032929/https://variety.com/2014/tv/news/titans-dick-grayson-nighwing-tnt-1201303968/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。至同年12月，由[[阿奇瓦·高斯曼|阿奇瓦·高斯曼]]編劇的試播集被預訂，講述主角[[迪克·格雷森|迪克·格雷森]]從[[蝙蝠俠|蝙蝠俠]]的助手[[羅賓_(漫畫)|羅賓]]成長為[[夜翼|夜翼]]，并組建[[少年泰坦|泰坦]]，其成員包括[[星火_(漫畫)|星火]]、[[渡鸦_(DC漫画)|渡鸦]]、[[芭芭拉·高登|芭芭拉·高登]]以及{{le|戰鷹與白鴿|Hawk and Dove}}。2015年中期，試播集在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[多倫多|多倫多]]拍攝<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/syfy-david-goyer-developing-superman-755060 |title=Syfy, David Goyer Developing Superman Origin Story ''Krypton'' |last=Goldberg |first=Lesley |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2014-12-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141223081805/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/syfy-david-goyer-developing-superman-755060 |archivedate=2014-12-13 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2018-12-10 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nerdist.com/vepisode/exclusive-which-dc-characters-will-be-on-tnts-the-titans/ |title=Exclusive: Which DC Characters Will Be On TNT's ''The Titans'' |work=Nerdist |last=Diaz |first=Eric |date=2015-02-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150202210414/http://www.nerdist.com/vepisode/exclusive-which-dc-characters-will-be-on-tnts-the-titans/ |archivedate=2015-02-02 |accessdate=2018-12-10 |language=en |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。2015年5月，特納電視台總裁凱文·賴利希望在正式拍攝開始之前確定演員，並且表示這部電視劇在非常忠實於漫畫的同時具有開創性<ref>{{cite web |url=http://renegadecinema.com/36840/teen-titans-tv-show-promises-to-remain-true-to-comics |title=''Teen Titans'' TV Show Promises to Remain True to Comics |first=Shawn S. |last=Lealos |work=Renegade Cinema |date=2015-02-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150519075733/http://renegadecinema.com/36840/teen-titans-tv-show-promises-to-remain-true-to-comics |archivedate=2015-05-19 |accessdate=2018-12-10 |language=en |deadurl=no}}</ref>。這部電視劇的名字由《泰坦》改為《黑鳥》，并計劃於2015年中期在多倫多開始拍攝<ref name="zero">{{cite web |url=http://season-zero.com/titans-creator-confirms-the-shooting-of-the-dc-comics-pilot/ |title=''Titans'' TNT Pilot DC Comics now entitled ''Blackbirds'' |work=Season Zero |author=Lulla |date=2015-06-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150922211604/http://season-zero.com/titans-creator-confirms-the-shooting-of-the-dc-comics-pilot/ |archivedate=2015-09-22 |accessdate=2018-12-10  |language=en |deadurl=no}}</ref>。之後，啟動製作的時間被延宕至2015年10月<ref>{{cite web |url=http://season-zero.com/titans-creator-confirms-the-shooting-of-the-dc-comics-pilot/ |title=''Blackbirds'' (''Titans'') TNT pilot from DC Comics postponed… |work=Season Zero |author=Luclla |date=2015-06-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150313211405/http://season-zero.com/titans-creator-confirms-the-shooting-of-the-dc-comics-pilot/ |archivedate=2015-03-13 |accessdate=2018-12-10 |language=en |deadurl=no}}</ref>。2016年1月，特納電視台宣佈不再繼續製作這一項目<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbr.com/dcs-live-action-titans-series-not-moving-forward-at-tnt/ |title=DC's Live-Action ''Titans'' Series Not Moving Forward at TNT |first=Brett |last=White |date=2016-01-07 |work=Comic Book Resources |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161106021401/http://www.cbr.com/dcs-live-action-titans-series-not-moving-forward-at-tnt/ |archivedate=2016-11-05 |accessdate=2018-12-10 |language=en |deadurl=no |quote=TNT president Kevin Reilly revealed that production on the long in-development drama series based on DC's ''Teen Titans'' property has been stopped.}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2016/tv/news/tnt-titans-dc-comics-series-dead-cancelled-1201674366/ |title=TNT Not Moving Forward with DC Comics Drama ''Titans'' |work=Variety |first=Whitney |last=Friedlander |date=2016-01-07 |accessdate=2018-12-10 |language=en |archive-date=2019-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190123050029/https://variety.com/2016/tv/news/tnt-titans-dc-comics-series-dead-cancelled-1201674366/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月，[[傑夫·強斯|傑夫·強斯]]表示：「[[DC漫畫|DC漫畫]]早已知曉特納電視台停止《泰坦》電視劇的製作，這已經不是新聞。我們有自己的《泰坦》開發計劃，是整個DC計劃的重要組成部分<ref name="Dade">{{cite web |url=http://tvline.com/2016/02/02/once-upon-a-time-spoilers-belle-season-5b/ |title=Matt's Inside Line: Scoop on ''Once'', ''Flash'', ''Lucifer'', ''Suits'', ''24'', ''Titans'', ''HTGAWM'', ''Castle'', ''NCIS: LA'' and More |work=TVLine |last=Mitovich |first=Matt Webb |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160626155811/http://tvline.com/2016/02/02/once-upon-a-time-spoilers-belle-season-5b/ |date=2016-02-02 |archivedate=2016-06-26 |accessdate=2018-12-10  |language=en |deadurl=no}}</ref>。」強斯補充道，「《泰坦》電視劇裡不能沒有[[羅賓_(漫畫)|羅賓]]……為此我們幕後做了很多工作<ref name="Dade" />。」之前這個項目正是因蝙蝠俠相關的版權問題而停滯<ref name="Dade" />。

2017年4月，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]宣佈《泰坦》會於2018年在DC漫畫的在線流媒體平台[[DC_Universe_(串流媒體)|DC Universe]]首播。該劇集由[[阿奇瓦·高斯曼|阿奇瓦·高斯曼]]、[[傑夫·強斯|傑夫·強斯]]、[[葛瑞格·貝蘭提|葛瑞格·貝蘭提]]以及莎拉·謝赫特開發製作，高斯曼和貝蘭提撰寫試播集劇本。製作公司除[[華納兄弟電視公司|華納兄弟電視公司]]之外，阿奇瓦·高斯曼的[[阿奇瓦·高斯曼|Weed Road Pictures]]和貝蘭提的{{le|Berlanti Productions}}亦參與其中<ref name="DeadlineAnnounce">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/04/dc-digital-service-titans-young-justice-outsiders-1202076831/ |title=DC Digital Service To Launch With ''Titans'' Series From Greg Berlanti & Akiva Goldsman And ''Young Justice: Outsiders'' |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |website=Deadline Hollywood |date=2017-04-25 |accessdate=2018-12-10 |language=en |archive-date=2019-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515020927/https://deadline.com/2017/04/dc-digital-service-titans-young-justice-outsiders-1202076831/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

