[[Polygon|多邊形]]網站劇評人蘇珊娜·馬洛認為《泰坦》「通過幽默元素緩和殘酷的暴力和黑暗的主題，並提供了足夠的時間深入挖掘主要角色故事以及相互關係<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.polygon.com/tv/2018/10/4/17935290/titans-dc-universe-review-nycc-2018|title=DC's ''Titans'' series review: There's more to it than 'F**k Batman'|website=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|first=Susana|last=Polo|date=2018-10-04|accessdate=2018-12-21|language=en|archive-date=2019-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190123050023/https://www.polygon.com/tv/2018/10/4/17935290/titans-dc-universe-review-nycc-2018|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。Comicbook網站的查利·瑞吉稱讚「{{le|安娜·迪奧普|Anna Diop}}運用精妙而真實的表演方式體現出角色神奇詭譎的經歷，同時傳達出隱藏在表面之下的兇猛與堅韌<ref>{{cite web|url=https://comicbook.com/dc/2018/10/03/titans-tv-review-dc-universe/|title=Review: ''Titans'' Is Campy, Violent, and Utterly Satisfying|website=Comicbook.com|first=Charlie|last=Ridgely|date=2018-10-04|accessdate=2018-12-21|language=en|archive-date=2018-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181213153651/https://comicbook.com/dc/2018/10/03/titans-tv-review-dc-universe/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。{{le|Nerdist|Nerdist Industries}}的羅茜·奈特認為劇中核心角色的選角讓人滿意，劇本也不錯<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://nerdist.com/dc-universe-titans-review/|title=DC Universe's ''Titans'' Is Surprising, Compelling, and Full of Great Characters|work=Nerdist|first=Rosie|last=Knight|date=2018-10-04|accessdate=2018-12-21|language=en|archive-date=2019-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109021428/https://nerdist.com/dc-universe-titans-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》撰稿人梅里爾·巴爾將《泰坦》與[[CW電視網|CW電視網]]的電視劇《[[河谷鎮_(電視劇)|河谷鎮]]》對比，稱《泰坦》的主題比以往設計少年泰坦的動畫系列更加黑暗以及堅韌<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/merrillbarr/2018/10/04/titans-review-nycc-dc-universe-akiva-goldsman-geoff-john-greg-berlanti-brenton-thwaites-anna-diop-teagan-croft-ryan-potter-rob-raven/#37de7cae23c9|title=''Titans'' Review: The ''Riverdale'' Of DC Comics Adaptations|last=Barr|first=Merrill|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=2018-10-04|accessdate=2018-12-21|language=en|archive-date=2018-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128124411/https://www.forbes.com/sites/merrillbarr/2018/10/04/titans-review-nycc-dc-universe-akiva-goldsman-geoff-john-greg-berlanti-brenton-thwaites-anna-diop-teagan-croft-ryan-potter-rob-raven/#37de7cae23c9|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

另一方面，[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]]網站的凱文·約曼對該節目中「過度暴力」持批評態度，他寫道，「《泰坦》整體上沒有賦予劇中的角色和[[超級英雄|超級英雄]]們任何新鮮的或特別扣人心弦的思想<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://screenrant.com/titans-tv-series-premiere-review-dc-universe-streaming/|title=''Titans'' Premiere Review: Mature Content Doesn't Make For Mature Storytelling|work=Screen Rant|first=Kevin|last=Yeoman|date=2018-10-04|accessdate=2018-12-21|language=en|archive-date=2018-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005123036/https://screenrant.com/titans-tv-series-premiere-review-dc-universe-streaming/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。類似地，[[Collider_(網站)|Collider]]網站的文尼·曼庫索表示，「如果你只是迷戀於影視中的老派極端暴力元素以及多變的敘事風格，《泰坦》並不是其中佼佼者<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://collider.com/titans-review/|title=''Titans'' Review: Teen Titans, No|work=[[Collider_(網站)|Collider]]|first=Vinnie|last=Mancuso|date=2018-10-04|accessdate=2018-12-21|language=en|archive-date=2018-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181220194722/http://collider.com/titans-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」

